article_title: Beshear encourages Kentuckians to shop for health insurance on Kynect starting Saturday
article_text: Gov. Steve Beshear encouraged Kentuckians on Monday to start shopping for health insurance as soon as this weekend on an improved kynect.ky.gov, the insurance exchange implemented under the federal Affordable Care Act.
